{"tid":801039,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【港女注意】「喜茶」香港開店 選址沙田新城市廣場","createTime":"2018-08-31T10:10:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T10:39:02.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"96fe91b86bde3a2f5e1e71fa962dfe442549510c","tid":801039,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:10:08.000Z","msg":"內地紅爆的飲品店「喜茶」，即將來香港開店，其官方IG帳戶凌晨公布，要往新加坡及香港開店，並開始在香港招聘員工，首間分店選址沙田新城市廣場。<br />\n喜茶在香港首間分店開設在沙田新城市廣場，但未有開店日期，但在IG留言已有一眾香港女生留言:「我要日日去飲！」喜茶在內地熱爆，排隊動輒超過半小時，製作茶時間亦要15至30分鐘，買一杯茶分分鐘要一小時，當中其「芝士芒芒」，售價為30元人民幣。<br />\n本報去年亦曾上深圳3間分店實測排隊，每間都要花40分鐘以上。<br />\n喜茶由內地90後聶雲宸創辦，他在1991年出生，畢業於廣東科學技術職業學院人文學院行政管理專業。大學畢業後，先開店賣手機，之後在年僅21歲時，於2012年在家鄉中山市開設第一家茶飲店「皇茶」。開業後他不斷修改配方，發現「芝士」這個概念特別受年輕人歡迎，於是首創出「芝士奶蓋」，產品大受歡迎。<br />\n因商標註冊問題，「皇茶」其後改名為「喜茶」，並在珠三角逐漸擴張，在2016年前開有50間分店，全部為直營店，而非加盟店，在今年分店數目已突破100間。在2016年，喜茶獲曾投資騰訊（700）、百度的風投基金IDG看中，注資1億元人民幣，在去年更已完成4億人民幣B輪融資，投資方為美團點評旗下龍珠資本。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535696970_125b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535696970_125b.jpg&h=8e46b9e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人劉先生（左一）由內地朋友帶來嘗試後表示，「飲落都幾好，好過喺香港」<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535696349_acba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535696349_acba.jpg&h=a469f0cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喜茶標榜是原味泡制，不加添加劑<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535696357_c9f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535696357_c9f8.jpg&h=225f0bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喜茶創辦人聶雲宸今年只有27歲<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535696349_0602.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535696349_0602.jpg&h=c56922f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聶雲宸曾表示要做「中國星巴克」。記者曾到深圳分店，裝潢佈置以時尚簡約為主<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535696356_22c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535696356_22c8.jpg&h=f48e6e75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n芝士芒芒一杯要30元人民幣<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180831/large/1535696349_9826.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180831%2Flarge%2F1535696349_9826.jpg&h=0a510abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喜茶去年更已完成4億人民幣B輪融資<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58628734\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58628734&d=ZLoo38Xlgln5pGjbkuEY%2BKNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=55d58a30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58628734&h=a1d16dfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180831/58628734</a><br />\n<br />\n屌 沙田咁遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b968246e18a2faca748f8d2c20be4ea6574cd0","tid":801039,"uid":176366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:30:53.000Z","msg":"WFC<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/31/183049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F31%2F183049_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=0f162cd2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d3fd59dfb78f41fbe4464a7c81db15be8c44cf0f","tid":801039,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:36:13.000Z","msg":"d名好柒 好想知間香港店會唔會用番同一個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b1ff0af5457ddf4e3ebdd459b96f8ce360c4cb3","tid":801039,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T10:39:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}